com.jme3.util
Class LittleEndien

java.lang.Object
  java.io.InputStream
      com.jme3.util.LittleEndien
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Closeable, java.io.DataInput
public class LittleEndien
extends java.io.InputStream
implements java.io.DataInput

LittleEndien is a class to read littleendien stored data via a InputStream. All functions work as defined in DataInput, but assume they come from a LittleEndien input stream. Currently used to read .ms3d and .3ds files.
